+ ./exist -h
exist - Sample application that uses the is.sh functions

Usage:
  exist FILENAME
  exist --help | -h
  exist --version | -v

Options:
  --help, -h
    Show this help

  --version, -v
    Show version number

Arguments:
  FILENAME
    The file to check if exists

Examples:
  exist somefile

